comment: Embiid (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds.
George (IND) puts a forearm into the body of Embiid (PHI) and affects his shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Teague (IND) hops consecutively on the same foot upon ending his dribble.
Embiid (PHI) maintains his right pivot until he releases his dribble.
Henderson (PHI) gets to the spot and jumps vertically and Embiid (PHI) does not make contact with George (IND) that affects his driving shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Embiid (PHI) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Teague (IND) commits a take foul on McConnell (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) turns into the body of Ellis (IND) and affects his driving shot attempt.
Teague (IND) makes marginal contact with Rodriguez (PHI) as the ball is knocked loose.
Henderson (PHI) makes contact with George (IND) that affects his SQBR.
Saric (PHI) makes marginal contact with Teague (IND) prior to the ball going OOB.
Embiid (PHI) does not dislodge Turner (IND) from his legal guarding position.
Turner (IND) puts a forearm into the body of Embiid (PHI) and affects his SQBR.
Allen (IND) holds Embiid (PHI) around the waist and affects his FOM in the post.
Allen (IND) makes contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm and affects his shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by IND before going out of bounds was upheld.
Allen (IND) tips the ball away and makes incidental contact with Saric (PHI) as they go to the floor.
Miles (IND) makes contact with Embiid (PHI) that affects his SQBR.
